original: Björkman, Göran Linus Gösta Rai-mundo, kyrkoherde. Ringas, f. 16/3/07 i Sthlm av förste aktuarien i komm:-koll., fil. dr Göran B. o. Ebba Frey. — Stud:ex. i Sthlm 26, teol. fil. ex. 28, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov samt prästv. f. Linköp. stift 31. V. kom-min. i Risinge 31, kyrkoadj. där 32, kommdn. i Järeda 36, utn. kyrkoh. i Odensvi 39, i Örtomta sed. 45.
translated: Björkman, Göran Linus Gösta Rai-mundo, vicar. Born March 16, 1907 in Stockholm to the first actuary of the municipal office, PhD Göran B. and Ebba Frey. He completed his secondary education in Stockholm in 1926, followed by theological studies and ordination in Linköping in 1931. He served as assistant vicar in Risinge in 1931, church adjutant there in 1932, vicar of Järeda in 1936, appointed vicar of Odensvi in 1939, and later in Örtomta from 1945 onwards. He married in the year 19xx (the information was not provided).
